    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クロエ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chloe</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ジュード</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Jude</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>げほっ、げほっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>*Cough, cough!*</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……ふむ。　死にかけたな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Ahem. I was about ready to die there.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なにを冷静に言ってるんだ！！
ホントに死ぬところだったんだぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you doing, speaking so composed?!!
You really were about to die!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なぜ泳げないのに
水の中に飛び込んだんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why did you jump into the water
even though you can't swim?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ウンディーネが一緒ならば
問題はなかったのだが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If Undine had been with me,
that wouldn't have been a problem.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>案外難しいものだな、泳ぎというのは</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Swimming is surprisingly tough.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんの確証もなしに飛び込んだのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you just jumped in without
concrete proof that you could do it?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どうもすみません……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm really sorry about her...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お前みたいなのは
一度痛い目をみないとわからないだろうな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Looks like someone like yourself won't learn
without going through hard lessons.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>溺れた時点で痛い目は見ていると思うのだが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think she already learned her lesson,
given that she nearly drowned...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>でもこいつ全然反省してないぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But she's got no remorse whatsoever!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>こうなったら
二度と馬鹿な真似しないように
俺が痛い目に遭わせてやる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In which case, I'll have to make her get it the hard
way, to make sure that never happens again!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
